Function Reference/get the author posts « WordPress Codex
-----------

Returns the total number of posts an author has published. Drafts and
private posts aren't counted. This tag must be used within [The
Loop](/The_Loop "The Loop").

Usage
-----

`  <?php echo get_the_author_posts(); ?> `

Example
-------

Displays the author's name and number of posts.

    <p><?php the_author(); ?> has blogged <?php echo number_format_i18n( get_the_author_posts() ); ?> 
    posts</p>

Harriett Smith has blogged 4,250 posts.

\

Parameters
----------

This tag does not accept any parameters.

